            <div class="title">
                Tshekedi Khama (Banishment)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-06-26/debates/c697aa9d-e934-4c05-8751-e51255346264/Furniture(MaximumPrices)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
