        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a638faea-f509-4539-b23c-1180fd5a897c">
                Mr. Sorensen  (Leyton)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a638faea-f509-4539-b23c-1180fd5a897c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-26/debates/71247eb7-c07e-4b46-a3ac-5cba64f61a31/TshekediKhama(Banishment)#contribution-a638faea-f509-4539-b23c-1180fd5a897c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would that principle also apply to Seretse Khama?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a638faea-f509-4539-b23c-1180fd5a897c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
