            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4ad98035-5910-47d7-9b7d-cb8c95120652">
                Mr. C. Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
