    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">But they must confine themselves to these four points—[HON. MEMBERS: "Oh!"]—I have a conscience.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4ad98035-5910-47d7-9b7d-cb8c95120652" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-26/debates/71247eb7-c07e-4b46-a3ac-5cba64f61a31/TshekediKhama(Banishment)#contribution-4ad98035-5910-47d7-9b7d-cb8c95120652">
