<p class="">Would due preparation be made for Tshekedi to go back with his case?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-56bb796e-53a6-4987-892c-21c9eed18004" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
