            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-00564662-480c-4cbd-8678-1dfa6c29860d">
                Mr. Gordon-Walker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-00564662-480c-4cbd-8678-1dfa6c29860d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-26/debates/71247eb7-c07e-4b46-a3ac-5cba64f61a31/TshekediKhama(Banishment)#contribution-00564662-480c-4cbd-8678-1dfa6c29860d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have given way to everybody so far.<p></p> I would beg the House to take all this into account, and to reject this Motion. The passing of the Motion tonight might have very grave consequences. Even if one put it no higher, it would be a very grave thing indeed to do. I beg the House, in the light of what I have said previously, and my suggestion about a further Kgotla to be attended by some Members of Parliament from both sides of this House, to decide that we ought to reject the Motion.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-00564662-480c-4cbd-8678-1dfa6c29860d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-26/debates/71247eb7-c07e-4b46-a3ac-5cba64f61a31/TshekediKhama(Banishment)#contribution-00564662-480c-4cbd-8678-1dfa6c29860d">
