            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-563ee5a1-344e-47df-8176-8dad83f4c0c4">
                Mr. Gordon-Walker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-563ee5a1-344e-47df-8176-8dad83f4c0c4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
