ea, W.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Crosland, C. A. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hoy, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Morrison, Rt. Hon. H. (Lewisham, S.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Grossman, R. H. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hubbard, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mort, D. L.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Cullen, Mrs. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, James (Ealing, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Moyle, A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Daines, P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Emrys (S. Ayrshire)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mulley, F. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dalton, Rt. Hon. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Hector (Aberdeen, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Murray, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Darling, George (Hillsborough)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Moelwyn (Islington, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Nally, W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Davies, A. Edward (Stoke, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hynd, H. (Accrington)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Neal, Harold (Bolsover)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Davies, Ernest (Enfield, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hynd, J. B. (Attercliffe)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Noel-Baker, Rt. Hon. P. J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Davies, Harold (Leek)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Irvine, A. J. (Edge Hill)</td></p><p class="Division"> 